text.section:
The Secretary of State shall prescribe and furnish on request forms for:
An application for a certificate of existence;
An application for a certificate of authority;
An amended application for a certificate of authority;
A certificate of withdrawal;
A change of registered office, registered agent, or both;
A change of principal address;
The resignation of the registered agent, the registered office, or both;
An application for a reserved name;
The renewal of a reserved name;
The transfer of a reserved name;
Name registration;
The annual report; and
An amendment to the annual report.
